thread.title: BRIEF-cBrain signs deal with Ministry of Immigration, Integration and Housing
thread.title_full: BRIEF-cBrain signs deal with Ministry of Immigration, Integration and Housing | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-cBrain signs deal with Ministry of Immigration, Integration and Housing
text:
Sept 14 Cbrain A/S :
* The Ministry of Immigration, Integration and Housing has signed an agreement with cBrain to deliver F2 case and document management
* F2 will be delivered as a cloud service (SaaS) from the F2 Cloud Center at the Danish Agency for Governmental IT services (Statens IT) Source text for Eikon:
